I '''Leon Marcus Uris''' (Agosto 3, 1924 – Junio 21, 2003) metung yuang Americanung nobelistang mekilala king piksyong pangkasalesayan ampo ing malalam nang pamanyalugsug a mibugnus kareng kayang nobela. Deng adua nang librung pekamasali (''bestselling'')  ila pin ding ''[[Exodus (nobela)|Exodus]]'' (milimbag anyang 1958) ampo ing ''[[Trinity (nobela)|Trinity]]'' (milimbag anyang 1976).<ref>"Author Leon Uris Dies at 78", ''The Elyria (Ohio) Chronicle Telegram'', June 25, 2003, p. A8.</ref>

